{"tid":1775762,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支持獨立檢討 朱敏健促警增透明度挽民望","createTime":"2019-12-09T05:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T05:32:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b9d3223ad351ed77073944ec141fad37ebba8912","tid":1775762,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:10:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191209/QB7ZALR2CKBU7ZPVLH33XXMRNQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191209%2FQB7ZALR2CKBU7ZPVLH33XXMRNQ%2F&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2LdRYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=feabd32b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191209%2FQB7ZALR2CKBU7ZPVLH33XXMRNQ%2F&h=087fd5df\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191209/QB7ZALR2CKBU7ZPVLH33XXMRNQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n支持獨立檢討<br />\n朱敏健促警增透明度挽民望<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191209/large/1575823012_0077.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191209%2Flarge%2F1575823012_0077.gif&h=a0f3b413&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱敏健<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特首林鄭月娥早前表示，將仿效英國處理2011年騷亂的手法，考慮設獨立檢討委員會審視持續半年反送中運動的成因。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：Pepe幽默抗爭：我食生命麵包<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n料監警會發中期報告<br />\n<br />\n監警會前秘書長朱敏健昨日出席公開活動後表示，反修例示威是影響香港的重大事件，因此他認為設獨立檢討委員會做法合理。他又認為，若警隊要挽回民望，應該盡量發佈資訊，「講得更多、更清楚」，令市民了解警方的行動理據。<br />\n<br />\n被問及監警會主席梁定邦近日接受內地傳媒訪問時表示，預料明年1月可公佈監警會反送中運動涉警方投訴的初步調查報告，指警隊只是執法部門，修例事件最初亦不是由警隊挑起，監警會將努力給香港警察和公眾一個公平的說法。<br />\n<br />\n朱敏健在回應時則指，梁定邦是基於所知的資料發表感受，不會損害監警會報告的公信力。<br />\n<br />\n朱敏健亦估計，監警會可能會發表中期報告以提升透明度。被問到監警會應否先評論7.21、8.31等單一事件，朱則指，要全面掌握事態發展才能作出公正結論，是否評論單一事件應交由監警會決定。<br />\n<br />\n■記者謝明明"},{"pid":"53ee10effd24563f0f045599cfbfb4cc11000397","tid":1775762,"uid":231480,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:10:49.000Z","msg":"係調查，唔係檢討<br />\n咪撚玩文字遊戲"},{"pid":"9162fb992bcf968fafdb33341362b5bc5db68cc5","tid":1775762,"uid":40415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:10:58.000Z","msg":"too late"},{"pid":"9aa0b14d1762b446a48c56ad78878998ae370d8c","tid":1775762,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53ee10effd24563f0f045599cfbfb4cc11000397","tid":1775762,"uid":231480,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:10:49.000Z","msg":"係調查，唔係檢討<br />\n咪撚玩文字遊戲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:12:12.000Z","msg":"其實檢討委員會好伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢擺明就想話示威者㗎啦 唔關警察事<br />\n睇吓英國嗰份報告你就明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e93802e62b829d7af8d07edc50d14c652c4ab4","tid":1775762,"uid":21920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:12:17.000Z","msg":"我檢你老母<br />\n咁殺左人剩係檢討唔洗負責啦"},{"pid":"b425fce95c206507574621fab43c23f7ccf663ff","tid":1775762,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:13:05.000Z","msg":"撒"},{"pid":"7330fbf2a52ce73833e75052b6ae3bcd6488acfa","tid":1775762,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53ee10effd24563f0f045599cfbfb4cc11000397","tid":1775762,"uid":231480,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:10:49.000Z","msg":"係調查，唔係檢討<br />\n咪撚玩文字遊戲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/g